  <h1>Website Wireframe</h1>

  <div class="description">
    <h2>Brief Write-Up</h2>
    <p>
      This document presents the wireframe sketches for my responsive website design. It includes three unique views:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Mobile View</strong>: Optimized for small screens with vertical stacking, touch-friendly navigation, and minimal layout.</li>
      <li><strong>Desktop View</strong>: Utilizes a multi-column layout, horizontal menu, larger content blocks, and enhanced visual hierarchy.</li>
      <li><strong>Landing Page</strong>: A distinct layout with a full-width hero image, intro text, and a call-to-action button designed to attract and guide users.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      All wireframes were created without color or typography styling, in accordance with wireframing best practices, and focus on content structure and layout clarity.
    </p>
  </div>

